IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.T_STPRPClockingHoursDetail') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_STPRPClockingHoursDetail
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_STPRPClockingHoursDetail (

	prp_clockinghoursdetail_id int,
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_division nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_costcentredescription nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_costcentrecode nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_teamname nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_employee nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_assignment nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_employeenumber nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_payroll nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_vendorempnumber nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_vendor nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_jobcategory nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_rate nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_date date,
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_week int,
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_shift nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_shifttime nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_calctime nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_clockin nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_clockout nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_approvalstatus nvarchar(4000),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_totinvval numeric(36,6),
	prp_clockinghoursdetail_finalflag int



	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/FINANCE/stprpclockinghoursdetail.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.T_STPRPClockingHoursDetail 
GO
